{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act28side", "eventName": "不義之財", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CV-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "獵人之夜", "storyInfo": "天氣越發寒冷，市民對銀行的怨憤也逐漸加深，有越來越多的人聚在銀行門口。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g7_sonwydowntown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們真的這麼早就要來嗎？現在銀行外面一個人也沒有啊。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有薄荷糖可以提神。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，但我想薄荷糖應該起不了什麼用，來，優等生，你來掐我一把。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "痛！", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開工吧。朋友們，都清醒點！哎，說的就是你！", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈……啾——抱、抱歉，芙蘭卡小姐。", "name": "黑鋼傭兵小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，接下來認真聽。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這間銀行總共有四個出口，貝尼，你帶四個人守在後門，小查，右邊就交給你和安妮了。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到！", "name": "黑鋼傭兵小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銅板，你和硬幣去車庫門。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到！", "name": "黑鋼傭兵小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的人，與我們三個一起留在正門……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，打擾了，女士，麻煩問下……", "name": "面色不悅的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們今天一天都會在這裡嗎？", "name": "面色不悅的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，是的，先生……不過我們只是站崗值勤，不會影響大家辦理業務。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辦理業務？前幾天我在這裡簽了一份拓荒協議，那是我最後一份業務。", "name": "面色不悅的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您是……？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……算是給他們的服務品質打個評分吧。", "name": "面色不悅的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（倒立大拇指）", "name": "面色不悅的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噗——", "name": "面色不悅的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這顆子彈……是你託潔西卡帶來的嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，幾年前我在維多利亞的一個古董店見到了它。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難怪你當時把營地翻了個遍也沒找到，現在想應該是某個軍官把那把銃偷偷帶去了維多利亞。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今銃已經沒了下落，這顆子彈是他僅存的遺物了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早告訴那傢伙不要在銃上搞那麼花裡胡哨的花紋了……這顆子彈你為什麼不自己留著？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起我，你才應該是那個保存它的人。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是覺得愧疚嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟朋友一場，最後如此收場，我也很難過。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你的愧疚與難過有用嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要什麼，伍迪？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喚回你的手下，停止驅趕居民。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，就算黑鋼離開，政府還會派其他的傭兵公司來，結局還是一樣。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本可以拒絕這項任務的，是嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鋼國際雖說是“國際”，可總部畢竟是在哥倫比亞，政府委派的任務，我們沒有什麼拒絕的權力。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來你也有要夾著尾巴做人的時候。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今時不同往日了，在哥倫比亞政府眼裡，我們這些武夫比不過那些特里蒙的精銳人才。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，大老闆，在這份與銀行還有政府的合約裡，黑鋼能得到什麼？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並不是份長久的合約，伍迪。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "政府提出要求，我們照做，事後拿報酬，除此外……我並不關心，也不容我關心。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得還在拉特蘭時，你總會和我講很多，大到國家間的摩擦，小到人群中的矛盾……那些因此而受苦的人們永遠是你的話題。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那都是很久遠的事了，伍迪，我記不得了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我記得很清楚，就在那段從圖書館到學生宿舍的路上，你告訴我，強大的人保護自己，偉大的人捍衛他人。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼到現在，親眼看到了那些人，你卻只會不冷不熱地講，不容關心，那便不關心了。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，我們都老了，能關心的東西非常有限。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我們都老了，還能關心的東西剩得不多……剩下的，都是最重要的東西了。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這一把殘破的老骨頭，保住地塊上所有人是不可能了，但身邊的人……我會死死守著。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我發誓，如果他們因為你的到來而受到傷害，那我會把這顆子彈原封不動地還給你。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我衷心希望，事情不會發展到那一步，伍迪。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g6_sonwydowntown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，人越聚越多了……要拉封鎖線嗎？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不到那一步。我們並不清楚人群的意圖，貿然行事只會更難控制情勢。如果可以溝通，我希望能先與組織者進行交涉。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……從凌晨到現在，大家都是陸陸續續地出現，不像有什麼組織的樣子。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也沒人帶著武器，看起來不像是要訴諸暴力，可我還是很擔心……", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我們的壓力自始至終都不在面前……而在身後。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回過頭，三人看向銀行明亮整潔的玻璃門窗。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玻璃的結實將外界灰暗、冰冷與融化的污雪阻擋在外。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但屋內的溫暖與明亮卻不會因為玻璃的透明，傾瀉到比銀行門下最後一層階梯更遠的地方。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，你看那個人是……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆娘……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g4_bank", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們中的大部分都已經簽下了拓荒協議，還聚在這幹什麼？", "name": "擔憂的銀行員工"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕什麼，黑鋼手裡的東西可不是吃素的。", "name": "冷漠的銀行員工"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是……唉，我電視都打開了，本來打算看看新年特別訪談的，也不知道今年州長會講些什麼。", "name": "擔憂的銀行員工"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，翻來覆去，不還是那些話。", "name": "冷漠的銀行員工"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觀眾朋友們，大家好。首先，我代表節目組，提前祝大家新年快樂。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本次節目我們將採訪的是州長先生，就本州居民關心的一系列問題向他提問——州長先生，您好。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來是我們節目的例行提醒——本次節目是在九月份錄製的，播放時的情況可能已經發生變化，敬請各位留意。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "責任全在特里蒙的科學家們。因為他們研究不出讓信使一天跑遍哥倫比亞的交通工具，我們只好提前三個月錄節目，不是嗎？", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g6_sonwydowntown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫娜女士，今天天氣這麼冷，你……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，但我今天哪裡也不會去。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道銀行與諸位之間的矛盾激烈……有訴求的話，或許可以由我向銀行轉達。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用緊張，雷蛇隊長。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來到這裡的人大多都已經簽署過拓荒協議了，等車隊到來，就離開了。你問我們還有什麼訴求，還想討要什麼……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有了。我們不會再做無用功了。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們來是為了什麼呢？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了看看。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看什麼？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小就被教導，在告別那些陪伴我們很久的人或者事物時，要好好再看一眼。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這陣子……我看過了自己的餐廳，看過了礦廠，看過了地塊上每一個地方。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而今天，在新年的第一天，我來看那個讓我不得不告別這一切的罪魁禍首。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫娜女士，請容我提醒你，每一份抵押協議都是你自己簽署的。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，沒錯，路是我們走的，也是你們指的……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無稽之談，就好比那位先生，我隱約記得，在他生意受挫四處借錢無門時，是我們為他發放了四萬的貸款。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，剛開始我欠你們四萬，這筆錢不大不小，我只想著趕緊還完。", "name": "氣憤的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你們又說，要合理規劃投資和負債，我不該一次性把錢連本帶利還清，你們提供分期優惠，我可以用剩下的錢買你們的理財產品……", "name": "氣憤的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，你們是借了我四萬，可最後我要付出的，卻是我的店鋪、房、車，甚至親人！", "name": "氣憤的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們當初相信了你們的宣傳。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們說，會讓我們的生活蒸蒸日上，幫助我們實現更加美好的未來……但你們規劃的所謂未來裡，我們這些客戶的位置又在哪裡？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我們是傻瓜，我們貪財，我們目光短淺，饞那一點甜頭，所以都上了鉤。", "name": "氣憤的地塊居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可女士，為什麼？為什麼整個地塊上所有人都像餓瘋了的鱗一樣，迫不及待要去咬那要命的鉤子？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的是我們自己的問題嗎？還是說，這片水塘從一開始就——", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷蛇小姐，請在十分鐘內將這群人疏散乾淨。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煩請盡快。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）潔西卡！想辦法給克里夫先生撥通電話，趕快！", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#7$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "潔西卡", "content": "我馬上……"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonebusy", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "潔西卡", "content": "不行，根本打不通……"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再試試……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，隊長，我得去當面告訴克里夫先生，這裡到底在發生什麼。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……去吧。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個……海倫娜女士，潔西卡已經去向高層匯報情況了，等一下應該……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想過自己的未來嗎，雷蛇小姐？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……一直想著要開一家保全公司。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會為了它貸款一筆錢嗎？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如有必要，我會，因為那是我一直想做的事情。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你可要小心了，那些錢只是以未來為名罷了，拿到它並不算觸碰到了未來。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是你保護著的那些人教會了我們這一點。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是竊賊，是騙子，他們在路牌上做手腳，卻反過來嘲笑我們走上了危險的夜路。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……明白，諸位。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "州長先生，我們不妨直接討論一些核心問題。眾所周知，在拓荒區和建成區之間，本州還存在著大量過渡區域——", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "區域內存在著的聚居點，大多是有幾十年歷史的拓荒地塊，有自己的支柱產業，但還不足以達到移動城市的標準，對吧？", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如您所說。我聽說，州政府最近在考慮這些地塊的處理問題。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "移動地塊是重要的戰略資源，但我不能苟同您的“處理”一詞，對過渡區及其居民的扶助早已成為州政府案頭最重要的事項之一。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "額外投資、稅收減免、入學優惠、低利貸款……過渡區居民們正從這些政策裡受益良多。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g4_bank", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經理……", "name": "擔憂的銀行員工"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去把那份授權協議拿出來，州政府發來的，緊急事態下授權給我們指揮私人武裝的那份。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是——", "name": "擔憂的銀行員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快去，別在這時候傻愣著。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g6_sonwydowntown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾十年前，我們的父輩來到此地，哥倫比亞的簽證官說想聽他們的夢想。", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，地塊的發展蓬勃，你們鼓勵我們走向美好的未來與明天，說整個哥倫比亞都想聽我們充滿幹勁的聲音。", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在我們身無分文，拖著病體，再無價值後，你們就把大門一關。", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有這樣的道理！我們會吶喊，我們會怒吼，我們會咆哮！", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你們最好豎起耳朵，聽好了。", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暴雪欲來，狂風將至♪", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們兩手空空，被推往荒野♪", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠離生長的土地♪", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找尋一抔屬於自己的土壤♪", "name": "激動的地塊居民"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於低利貸款……", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在遲疑？這很罕見，我以為您還會不停地用問題轟炸我。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不瞞您說，我確實認為這是一個很尖銳的問題，希望您能如實回答。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一些人認為，減免貸款利息是在用稅收補貼當地經濟，不僅可能讓錢打水漂，還可能傷害當地居民自力更生的積極性，使他們變得懶惰。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為州政府，我們確實在一些地塊發現了類似的情況，但我們也要向其他公民呼籲，請多給過渡區一些時間。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請相信，當地的居民並非懶惰，而是需要更多的時間，來學習如何重新利用自己的雙腿行走。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當他們強壯到足以丟掉拐杖的那一天，他們會如數還清款項，並感激我們的慷慨和哥倫比亞公民間的兄弟之情。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g4_bank", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scroll", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡，經理！", "name": "擔憂的銀行員工"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去把窗戶都關好，關閉窗簾，離門窗遠一點。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們這……是在外面唱歌嗎？", "name": "擔憂的銀行員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g6_sonwydowntown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從耕田到掄錘♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切這些事情都是我們完成的♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們誕生起就♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注定要永遠負重前行♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十分鐘到了，既然他們執意不肯離開，我們應該採取更強硬的措施。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，女士，做不到。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#4$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們之間的關係本不應該如此難堪的。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們執意怠忽職守，那我只能遺憾地通知你，這支小隊現在交由我來指揮。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你算什麼東——", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#8$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回收地塊的協議是由政府、銀行與黑鋼三方共同簽署，裡面條約寫明，黑鋼分派來的人手在特殊情況下須聽從我們的指揮調度。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是當時發來的授權書，請雷蛇小姐過目。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您無權越級指揮我們的行動，女士。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "xTo": 80.0, "duration": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 80.0, "duration": 60.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這上面寫得一清二楚，我有權力。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動手吧，雷蛇小姐。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請恕我拒絕。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您現在拒絕的可不是一間小小銀行的請求，而是政府的命令。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要忘記幫助黑鋼走到現在的是什麼，是哥倫比亞傾注在你們身上的信任。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……信任很容易崩塌，一次小小的失約，就足以重創搭建好的一切。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動手，我不想再多說了，雷蛇小姐。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "挨餓的是我們，送死的是我們♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了空頭支票付出一切的是我們♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但未來……未來卻沒有我們♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見了，家鄉♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將遠離生長的土地♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只為找尋一抔屬於自己的土壤♪", "name": "地塊居民"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，你再說多少次都沒有用。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會開火。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重複一遍，我不會開火，也不會允許我小隊的任何一個成員開火。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的任務僅是確保無人衝進銀行，傷害到你們寶貴的生命。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我判斷，他們對你們的生命安全沒有任何威脅，只想和你們作一場告別。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們脆弱的心靈因此受傷，那我深表同情。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟……離別總是傷感的，對吧？", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家聽好，沒有我的命令，都不許擅動。", "name": "雷蛇"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到……", "name": "通訊器"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到！", "name": "通訊器"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收、收到……", "name": "通訊器"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到。", "name": "通訊器"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回去吧，女士，這是真實的歌聲，多聽聽沒壞處。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}